---

<section
    class="relative h-screen pt-20 2xl:pt-0 items-start lg:items-center 2xl:items-center flex justify-between bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-900 to-sky-700 text-white px-4 sm:px-6 w-full"
>
    <ul class="circles absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li>
        <li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li>
    </ul>

    <div
        class="relative z-10 w-[90%] 2xl:w-[80%] mx-auto flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between gap-12"
    >
        <!-- Texto -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 text-center lg:text-left space-y-6">
            <h1
                class="text-3xl lg:text-7xl 2xl:text-8xl font-extrabold leading-tight relative inline-block"
            >
                Bienvenido
                <span
                    class="absolute px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-600 text-black text-sm font-semibold -top-4 -right-16 transform rotate-12"
                >
                    S.I.H
                </span>
            </h1>

            <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-gray-300 font-semibold">
                <span class="text-amber-600">Sistema POS</span> control ventas e
                inventario
            </p>

            <p
                class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-200 font-light leading-relaxed"
            >
                - Potencia tu negocio con nuestra solución integral. <br />
                Gestiona tus productos y ventas con un sistema POS avanzado,<br
                />
                integrado con absoluto
                <span
                    class="text-[#003092] bg-white/70 rounded-2xl px-2 font-medium"
                >
                    control total y eficiente.
                </span>
            </p>

            <a
                href="#contacto"
                class="w-36 mt-4 btn text-[#003092] bg-white/70 border-none p-2 flex justify-center items-center rounded-full font-semibold shadow-md transition-transform hover:scale-105"
            >
                ¡Prueba Gratis!
            </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Imagen y blobs -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center relative">
            <!-- Blobs -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
                <div
                    class="animate-blob absolute left-5 top-0 h-64 w-64 bg-[#9675D0] opacity-40 mix-blend-multiply blur-3xl rounded-full"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="animate-blob animation-delay-2000 absolute right-5 top-32 h-72 w-72 bg-[#fdc6bb] opacity-50 mix-blend-multiply blur-3xl rounded-full"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="animate-blob animation-delay-4000 absolute bottom-0 left-1/3 h-64 w-64 bg-[#7ec7b1] opacity-50 mix-blend-multiply blur-3xl rounded-full"
                >
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Imagen hover -->
            <div
                class="relative group w-full max-w-xs sm:max-w-md 2xl:max-w-xl"
            >
                <img
                    src="fondo1.png"
                    class="w-full transition-opacity duration-500 group-hover:opacity-0 z-10 relative drop-shadow-2xl"
                    alt="Computadora"
                />
                <img
                    src="fondo2.png"
                    class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500 group-hover:opacity-100 z-0"
                    alt="Computadora Hover"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
